design:
Update .claude/settings.json (project-level) to add:
{
  "hooks": {
    "PostToolUse": [{
      "matcher": "Bash",
      "hooks": [{
        "type": "command",
        "command": "sl session capture"
      }]
    }]
  }
}
This should be added to the existing settings, not replace them. If the project uses .claude/settings.local.json, add there instead to avoid committing to git. Reference quickstart.md for the hook configuration format.
